有我係度隻狗死硬」，甚麼「捷克嘅係scorpion非常好用嘅槍」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來，連登內外充滿了快活的空氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdYfLXw.png&amp;h=2f645353&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa31ng6V.jpg&amp;h=8ea8c023&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xyeMeVf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxyeMeVf.png&h=415b76dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu3xXmHV.png&amp;h=ce7dfffa&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFiooneH.png&amp;h=a27668c0&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhFuDrg9.png&amp;h=008b0eb8&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOBQ2Kjk.png&amp;h=1791741f&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n]<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2123380/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2123380/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2155320/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2155320/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v0wuGwk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv0wuGwk.png&h=877531f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vBGk3V.png&amp;h=939ee994&amp;s=540\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5a1ed1115987acb18d95719abb01196f643413e7","tid":2219513,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T23:26:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63446fc2155797fbccb5513c4106a919281758fe","tid":2219513,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5897d6a2cbea599d8401f7876eb9cb2dc7e27503","tid":2219513,"uid":146642,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"8ca3ba284853fa90c6ed4753b31f1dc5f2c65877","tid":2219513,"uid":273703,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{